author: Fiona Denton
description:
Kingfisher might be one of the most productive authors in the world. Snake-Eater is her fifth release of 2025 and, as usual, has proven to be a delicious reading treat. More in the vein of her fantasy-horror stories like A House with Good Bones, but not quite as dark as ones like The Hollow Places, […]
